"content": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is an excerpt from a review article I read. This article was published in a prestigious journal by an expert of the field. Yet it degenerated into simple name-calling.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I experienced first-hand a very harsh review of a paper I submitted. It is not a rejection perhaps out of pity for me?</p>\n",
